summary: Fashionable lingerie body replacer for those that don\'t want nudity.
descriptionHtml:
[color=red]This mod is ancient, there are new and better things now, and as such I\'m no longer offering support for it.[/color]

Lace Up Lingerie
by XunAmarox
Version: 1.0

Description:
Non-nude body replacer featuring a stylish pink micro lace up thong and lace bra.

This will replace your default female body, for you and every NPC in the game.

Installation:
1. Paste contents of /Data/ into /Data/
2. Enjoy!

Uninstallation:
1. Figure out what you pasted into your Data folder.
2. Delete it.
3. Stop enjoying. :)

Included:
body (lingerie) texture
normal map
shader map
hand texture

Nothing else. Probably won\'t work for anything that doesn\'t use the default female texture.

Version History:
1.0 - Release
